name: Js-euchre
body:
An attempt at an HTML 5 and Javascript only implementation of Euchre.

Hope to eventually support some AI players as well as two on two human players.

Not much done yet...but working on it in spare time, more as a learning excercise.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
tagline: An attempt at a completely HTML5/JS Based euchre game.  Used as a personal learning excercise
